Argentina Budget Sees Up to $7.5 Billion Debt Fund, Ambito Says

-- B y   B i l l   F a r i e s
-- 
2011-09-16T15:53:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/argentina-budget-sees-up-to-7-5-billion-debt-fund-ambito-says.html
Argentina ’s draft 2012 budget calls
for authorization to use up to $7.5 billion in central bank
reserves to pay debt, Ambito Financiero reported, without saying
how it obtained the information.  Argentina’s government was due to send the draft budget to
Congress yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
